-ai-bots-spam-resume-cover-letter-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehundreds%20of%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20guarantee%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20will%20ever%20be%20reviewed%20by%20a%20hiring%20manager%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20get%20discouraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECareer%20coach%20Shari%20Santoriello%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20in%20the%20industry%20for%2025%20years%2C%20knows%20it%3B%20she%20sees%20it%20all%20the%20time.%20So%20when%20her%20clients%20come%20to%20her%20asking%20how%20to%20streamline%20their%20job%20hunt%20and%20make%20the%20process%20easier%20but%20still%20optimized%20to%20draw%20the%20most%20eyes%2C%20she's%20a%20wealth%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20tips%20she%20gives%20her%20clients%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-get-job-this-year-network-resume-skills-certificates-unemployment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20their%20job%20search%20simpler%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f40e075-9898-4dcb-b615-8d4bdddd4a73%5C%22%3ECreate%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20vault%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20we%20think%20of%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20as%20being%20set%20in%20stone%2C%20when%20Santoriello%20says%20it's%20a%20dynamic%20piece%20of%20material%20for%20a%20job%20seeker%20%E2%80%94%20it%20should%20be%20flexible%20and%20adaptable%20for%20every%20job%20you're%20applying%20for.%20She%20noted%20that%20nobody%20likes%20to%20hear%20that%2C%20but%20you%20can%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20yourself%20by%20creating%20what%20some%20people%20call%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20vault%20or%20master%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20vault%20is%20a%20living%20document%20listing%20all%20your%20past%20jobs%20and%20accomplishments%20that%20you%20can%20select%20from.%20So%2C%20when%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-shares-resume-tips-avoid-vague-statements-quantify-achievements-2024-2%5C%22%20target%