India%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20in%20the%20headlines%20constantly%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months.%20Ever%20since%20his%20transfer%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20especially%20as%20captain%2C%20the%20charismatic%20cricketer%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%2C%20mostly%20for%20wrong%20reasons.%20The%20veteran%20cricketer%20failed%20to%20inspire%20Mumbai%20Indians%20side%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024%2C%20finishing%20bottom%20of%20the%2010-team%20points%20table.%20However%2C%20Hardik%20seemed%20to%20be%20getting%20back%20to%20his%20old%20form%2C%20having%20scored%2023-ball%2040%20for%20India%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20warm-up%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20secured%20a%2050-run%20win%20in%20their%20only%20practice%20match%2C%20Hardik%20took%20the%20plaudits%20for%20his%20brilliant%20hitting%20as%20a%20finisher.%20After%20the%20game%2C%20the%20all-rounder%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20'difficult'%20times%20he%20faced%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEventually%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20you%20have%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20battle.%20Sometimes%20life%20puts%20you%20in%20situations%20where%20things%20are%20tough%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20that%20if%20you%20leave%20the%20game%20or%20the%20field%2C%20the%20battle%20that%20is%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20what%20you%20want%20from%20your%20sport%2C%20or%20the%20results%20you%20are%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Hardik%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20yeah%2C%20it%20has%20been%20difficult%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20have%20been%20process-driven%2C%20I%20have%20tried%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20routines%20I%20used%20to%20follow%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports%2C%20the%20brodacster%20of%20T20