%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fts8c76eg_annamalai-fact-check-_625x300_02_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFact%20Check%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewsMeter%20found%20that%20the%20claim%20is%20misleading%20as%20the%20video%20clip%20has%20been%20edited%20to%20remove%20the%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20using%20relevant%20keywords%2C%20we%20found%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DERNkMQs1n28%26t%3D388s%5C%22%3Eextended%20version%20of%20the%20clip%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20YouTube%20channel%20Inside%20Tamil%20titled%20'Thiru.%20Annamalai%20l%20Press%20Meet%20l%20BJP%20l%20Savarkar%20Book%20Published.'%20It%20was%20published%20on%20October%202%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20shows%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20book%20on%20Savarkar%20for%20which%20Annamalai%20was%20the%20chief%20guest.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FFoundationPK%2Fstatus%2F1442767576795205633%5C%22%3EPrabha%20Khaitan%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20book's%20publisher%2C%20shared%20the%20details%20of%20the%20book%20launch%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%206%3A28-minute%20mark%20in%20the%20YouTube%20video%2C%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20media%20question%20about%20Savarkar%2C%20Annamalai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20when%20people%20discuss%20Veer%20Savarkar%2C%20they%20often%20criticise%20him%20right%20away.%20They%20call%20him%20an%20apologist.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20use%20that%20word.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20they%20usually%20say%20British%20boot%20licker.%20People%20say%20that%20Veer%20Savarkar%20licked%20the%20boots%20of%20the%20Englishman.%20But%20does%20that%20comment%20really%20do%20justice%20to%20the%20man%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20clip%20only%20featured%20Annamalai's%20'boot%20lick'%20statement%20while%20editing%20out%20the%20context%20making%20it%20look%20like%20he%20was%20criticising%20Savarkar.%20However%2C%20throughout%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20Annamalai%20could%20be%20seen%20stating%20that%20Savarkar%20was%20innocent%20and%20that%20his%20actions%20were%20not%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FERNkMQs1n28%3Fsi%3Dbcg9ycE19NnaYifT%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20sharing%20the%20clip%20claim%20that%20Annamalai%20made%20the%20'negative%20comments'%20about%20Savarkar%20before%20joining%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bjp.org%2Fphoto-gallery%2Fphotographs-former-ips-officer-k-annamalai-joining-bjp%5C%22%3EAnnamalai%20joined%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20August%2025%2C%202020%2C%20and%20the%20video%20is%20from%202021%2C%20a%20year%20after%20he%20joined%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20video%20of%20Annamalai%20'criticising'%20Savarkar%20is%20edited%20and%20is%20being%20shared%20without%20context.%20The%20claim%20is%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaim%20Review%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20video%20shows%20TN%20BJP%20state%20president%20K%20Annamalai%20making%20disparaging%20remarks%20about%20Savarkar%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20'boot%20licker%20of%20the%20British.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaimed%20By%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaim%20Reviewed%20By%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20NewsMeter%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaim%20Source%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20X%20users%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClaim%20Fact%20Check%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20False%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFact%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20claim%20is%20misleading.%20In%20the%20original%20extended%20video%2C%20Annamalai%20was%20refuting%20alle