development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Contest%20Evolved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20by%20then%20ten-month-old%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20was%20still%20to%20take%20baby%20steps%20towards%20getting%20election-ready.%20The%20Congress%20was%20tottering%20from%20the%20rout%20in%20the%20December%20assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20it%20fought%20alone%20to%20improve%20its%20tactical%20nous%20in%20the%20national%20poll%20seat%20distribution.%20Two%20opposition%20chief%20ministers%20were%20in%20jail%2C%20most%20crucially%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20arguably%20the%20closest%20Modi%20clone%20in%20populism%20and%20political%20style%20and%20substance.%20And%20the%20Congress's%20finances%20were%20hobbled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-how-congress-and-bjps-campaigns-have-evolved-5720178%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20How%20Congress%20And%20BJP's%20Campaigns%20Evolved%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20perennials%20were%20in%20place%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20personal%20popularity%20continued%20to%20be%20stratospheric.%20Nationalism%20had%20become%20co-terminus%20with%20Hinduism.%20The%20Ram%20Mandir%20%26quot%3BPran%20Pratishtha%26quot%3B%20with%20Modi%20as%20virtually%20the%20high%20priest%20was%20fresh%20in%20memory.%20The%20perception%20had%20taken%20root%20that%20Modi%20had%20enhanced%20India's%20prestige%20in%20the%20world.%20New%20welfarism%20deliverables%20had%20undoubtedly%20improved%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20of%20all%20recipients%2C%20transcending%20communities.%20Digital%20payments%20had%20become%20so%20ubiquitous%20even%20the%20lowliest%20tradesman%20found%20commerce%20a%20dream.%20Vast%20improvements%20in%20physical%20infrastructure%20had%20solidified%20support%20among%20the%20middle%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Unexpectedly%20Tough%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20the%20Election%20Commission%20obliged%20with%20a%2044-day%2C%20seven-phase%20election%20schedule%20that%20would%20enable%20the%20far%20better-resourced%20BJP%20to%20optimise%20the%20showcasing%20of%20its%20one-point%20election%20plank%3A%20Modi%20and%20his%20guarantees.%20A%20confident%20Modi%2C%20secure%20in%20the%20strongholds%20of%20the%20North%20and%20the%20West%2C%20was%20busy%20storming%20the%20South%20and%20declaring%20in%20Parliament%20%26quot%3BAbki%20Baar%20400%20par%26quot%3B%20anticipating%20a%2010%25%20increase%20in%20its%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20unexpectedly%20hard-fought%20win%20will%20have%20two%20main%20reasons%3A%20Modi's%20superior%20tactical%20nous%20after%20the%20bulge%20had%20sounded%20and%20the%20Opposition's%20failure%20to%20spot%20and%20capitalise%20on%20the%20full%20entrails%20of%20the%20widespread%20but%20simmering%20anti-incumbency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20tepid%20first%20phase%2C%20Modi%20realised%20that%20if%20he%20was%20to%20get%20the%2050%25%20of%20the%20Hindu%20vote%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20get%204%2F10%20votes%20nationally%20(Hindus%20being%2080%25%20of%20the%20population)%2C%20Hindutva%2C%20and%20relentless%20charges%20of%20appeasement%20of%20the%20Muslims%20by%20the%20Congress%20had%20to%20be%20the%20main%20refrain.%20This%20despite%20more%20than%20one%20credible%20poll%20showing%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20people%20who%20believed%20that%20India%20belonged%20to%20more%20than%20one%20religion%20was%20not%20much%20less%20than%20Modi's%20popularity%20rating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20electorally%20important%20for%20Modi%20to%20don%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20Samrat%3C%2Fem%3E%20crown%20was%20to%20seal%20the%20loyalty%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20Sangh%20Parivar%20cadres%2C%20chiefly%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20Modi's%20popularity%20among%20these%20cadres%20far%20outstrips%20that%20among%20the%20collectivist%20Nagpur%20leadership.%20But%20the%20RSS%20cadres'%20resolve%20was%20wavering%20because%20the%20BJP's%20primacy%20to%20the%20winnability%20criterion%20meant%20widely%20that%20they%20were%20now%20canvassing%20for%20somebody%20they%20had%20reviled%20till%20the%20other%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Shaky%20Opposition%2C%20Initially%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20reason%20why%20the%20BJP%20will%20scrape%20through%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Opposition%20ineptitude%20and%20lack%20of%20a%20counter-narrative.%20While%20INDIA%20and%20ally%20leaders%20-%20Mamata%2C%20Sidharamiah%20et%20al%20-%20have%20now%20worked%20out%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20welfarism%2C%20wooing%20the%20poor%20and%20especially%20the%20women%20with%20the%20same%20effective%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfers%20(DBTs)%20as%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20have%20yet%20to%20acquire%20the%20development%20credentials%20of%20Modi.%20Revenue%20buoyancy%20has%20enabled%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20sharply%20step%20up%20capital%20expenditure.%20With%20his%20demonstrable%20commitment%20to%20using%20technology%20in%20governance%2C%20Modi%20still%20has%20the%20edge%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20representing%20the%20aspirational%20in%20the%20average%20Indian%2C%20most%20so%20among%20the%20young.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20widespread%20sentiment%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESarkar%20toh%20Modi%20hi%20banayega%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20if%20nothing%20then%20through%20its%20ruthless%20use%20of%20SDDB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-why-a-2004-like-scenario-is-unlikely-5684511%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Why%20A%202004-Like%20Scenario%20Is%20Unlikely%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20how%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20spoiler%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20is%20contesting%20all%2080%20seats%2C%20but%20unlike%20in%202019%2C%20none%20of%20its%20candidates%20is%20expected%20to%20win.%20With%2014%20Muslim%20candidates%2C%20it%20is%20the%20party%20with%20the%20most%20candidates%20from%20the%20community.%20Upshot%3F%20Behenji%20can%20be%20safely%20expected%20to%20split%20the%20non-BJP%20votes%20in%20enough%20contentious%20constituencies%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20retain%20its%2062%2F80%20score%20of%202019%2C%20despite%20the%20last-minute%20spurt%20in%20popular%20support%20for%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress-Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20alliance.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20outreach%20beyond%20his%20Yadav-Muslim%20support%20base%2C%20where%20only%20nine%20tickets%20were%20given%20to%20MY%20(Muslims-Yadav)%20candidates%20and%20many%20more%20to%20other%20OBCs%2C%20will%20go%20down%20as%20another%20instance%20of%20too%20little%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pressure%20On%20BJP%20To%20React%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20these%20seven%20weeks%20have%20also%20rebounded%20on%20the%20BJP%20because%20it%20gave%20space%20for%20all%20the%20deep%20fault%20lines%20and%20failures%20in%20India's%20polity%20the%20time%20and%20scope%20to%20manifest%20themselves%20through%20the%20concentrated%20political%20mobilisation%20that%20elections%20engender.%20And%20for%20all%20its%20faults%2C%20the%20Opposition%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20or%20just%20buoyed%20by%20spontaneous%20local%20dissatisfaction%2C%20has%20done%20what%20seemed%20impossible%20some%20time%20ago%3A%20set%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20public%20discourse%20forcing%20the%20BJP%20to%20react.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENowhere%20was%20this%20more%20successful%20than%20in%20creating%20the%20fear%20among%20the%20Dalits%20that%20the%20BJP%20war%20cry%20of%20%26quot%3B400%26quot%3B%20par%20was%20intended%20to%20curb%20reservations.%20This%20threatened%20the%20BJP's%20social%20engineering%20among%20Dalits%20where%20its%20sustained%20work%20of%20coopting%20Dalits%20into%20the%20Hindu%20fold%20has%20electorally%20focused%20on%20successfully%20wooing%20the%20non-dominant%20and%20more%20populous%20Dalit%20sub-castes%2C%20pitting%20them%20against%20the%20BSP's%20base%20of%20Jatavs%20and%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India's%20(RPI)%20Mahars.%20The%20Congress's%20promise%20to%20scrap%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20and%20institute%20a%20massive%20one-year%20apprentice%20scheme%20tapped%20effectively%20into%20the%20desperation%20among%20youth%20for%20jobs%2C%20most%20so%20among%20the%20educated%20lot.%20For%20a%20brief%20moment%2C%20there%20was%20a%20flash%20of%20the%202004%20%26quot%3Bclass%26quot%3B%20election%2C%20BJP's%20biggest%20nightmare.%20However%2C%20these%20ripples%20came%20too%20late%20to%20whip%20up%20the%20widespread%20despair%20and%20disillusionment%20into%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20BJP%20Now%20Needs%20To%20Focus%20On%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%2010%20years%20have%20been%20rightly%20applauded%20for%20broadly%20good%20macro%20management%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20a%20distinct%20reduction%20in%20poverty%2C%20thanks%20to%20%26quot%3Bnew%20welfarism%26quot%3B%20and%20free%20food%20for%20800%20million%20people.%20But%20the%20needle%20has%20barely%20moved%20on%20several%20key%20ground%20realities%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20deeply%20disappoint%20India's%20increasingly%20aware%20and%20aspirational%20society%2C%20and%20it's%20anybody's%20guess%20when%20these%20frustrations%20will%20erupt%20into%20street%20agitations.%20Arguably%2C%20the%20readiest%20powder%20keg%20is%20farmer%20unrest.%20The%20government%20refuses%20to%20recognise%20that%20farmers%20believe%2C%20with%20good%20reason%2C%20that%20the%20MSP%20is%20their%20only%20bulwark%20against%20their%20occupational%20hazards%20and%20lack%20of%20parity%20in%20market%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuality%20school%20education%20and%20universal%20healthcare%20are%20chimaeras%2C%20even%20though%20proven%20models%20for%20both%20exist%20in%20states%3B%20the%20now%20four-year-old%20New%20Education%20Policy%20rots%20on%20the%20shelf.%20The%20extent%20of%20child%20malnutrition%20and%20stunting%20is%20a%20shame%20for%20a%20lower-middle-income%20country.%20Thirty%20years%20after%20the%20passage%20of%20Articles%2071%20and%2072%2C%20the%20empowerment%20of%20local%20self-governing%20institutions%20is%20a%20mirage.%20Widespread%20digitalisation%20notwithstanding%2C%20pervasive%20corruption%20for%20the%20average%20Indian%20is%20no%20less%20an%20albatross.%20The%20bureaucracy%20still%20rules%20and%20not%20serves%2C%20early%20gains%20of%20the%20Karmayogi%20Mission%20notwithstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20growing%20formalisation%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20youth%20are%20mostly%20stuck%20in%20jobs%20with%20sustenance%20wages%20and%20little%20dignity%20and%20purpose.%20The%20appalling%20lack%20of%20progress%20in%20skilling%20continues%20to%20threaten%20to%20turn%20the%20demographic%20dividend%20into%20a%20demographic%20disaster.%20The%20economy's%20potential%20continues%20to%20be%20hobbled%20by%20low%20consumer%20demand%20growth%20because%20of%20the%20'K'%20nature%20of%20economic%20recovery%2C%20where%20inequality%20has%20catapulted.%20A%20stunted%20investment-to-GDP%20ratio%20is%20propped%20up%20only%20by%20hugely%20stepped-up%20government%20capital%20spending%2C%20while%20private%20sector%20capital%20investment%20awaits%20a%20revival%20of%20widespread%20consumer%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaking%20Everyone%20Along%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20change%20in%20any%20one%20or%20more%20of%20these%20vectors%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20would%20have%20changed%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20of%20a%20sufficiently%20large%20number%20of%20Indians%20for%20Modi%20to%20get%20his%20%26quot%3B400%20paar%26quot%3B.%20Ready%2C%20proven%20solutions%20to%20many%20of%20these%20structural%20problems%20exist%20with%20this%20government%2C%20in%20other%20than%20the%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20engine%26quot%3B%20states%20and%20among%20experts%20with%20no%20known%20political%20affiliations.%20Economist%20Kartik%20Muralidharan's%20opus%20%3Cem%3EAccelerating%20India's%20Development%3A%20A%20State-Led%20Roadmap%20for%20Effective%20Governance%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20ready%20solutions%20for%20a%20dramatic%20improvement%20in%20state%20capacity%2C%20a%20pre-requisite%20for%20realising%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20India's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202026%20delimitation%2C%20arguably%20the%20biggest%20national%20iceberg%20ahead%2C%20cannot%20be%20a%20take-it-or-leave-it%20exercise.%20Modi%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20good%20listener%2C%20who%20gives%20extended%20time%20for%20solutions%20to%20problems%20he%20is%20interested%20in.%20Elections%20over%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20taking%20everyone%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ajay%20Kumar%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20He%20is%20former%20Managing%20Editor%2C%20Business%20Standard%20and%20former%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717301100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2j2ju7l_narendra-modi_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-2024-looking-back-looking-ahead-5798176%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20good%20listener%2C%20who%20gives%20extended%20time%20for%20solutions%20to%20problems%20he%20is%20interested%20in.%20Elections%20over%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20taking%20everyone%20along.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-2024-looking-back-looking-ahead-5798176%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea%20drops%20600%20more%20'trash-filled'%20balloons%20in%20South%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%