final%20combination%20might%20look%20like.%20Going%20by%20that%20logic%2C%20the%20India%20vs%20Bangladesh%20T20%20World%20Cup%20warm-up%20match%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20hint%20about%20India's%20playing%20XI%20going%20forward.%20The%20major%20talking%20point%20was%20who%20would%20partner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20opener%20when%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20action%20starts%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20on%20June%205%20against%20Ireland.%20There%20were%20two%20choices%20-%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20did%20not%20play%20the%20match.%20Something%2C%20which%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20was%20due%20to%20fatigue.%20%26quot%3BVirat%20has%20just%20arrived%20yesterday%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20miss%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%20However%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20was%20there.%20Interestingly%2C%20seven%20Indian%20batters%20got%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20conditions%20but%20designated%20opener%20Jaiswal%20did%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20that%20mean%2C%20he%20won't%20be%20the%20first-choice%20opener%20in%20the%20upcoming%20matches%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20did%20not%20answer%20the%20question%20directly%2C%20but%20did%20talk%20about%20the%20line-up%20of%20the%20side%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuite%20happy%20with%20how%20things%20went.%20Pretty%20much%20got%20what%20we%20wanted%20from%20the%20game.%20Like%20I%20said%20at%20the%20toss%2C%20it%20was%20important%20to%20get%20used%20to%20th