-open-message-clear-after-t20-world-cup-warm-up-rohit-sharmas-big-hint-5796821%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fno-yashasvi-jaiswal-virat-kohli-to-open-message-clear-after-t20-world-cup-warm-up-rohit-sharmas-big-hint-5796821%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fno-yashasvi-jaiswal-virat-kohli-to-open-message-clear-after-t20-world-cup-warm-up-rohit-sharmas-big-hint-5796821%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Sunita%20Williams'%20Boeing%20Space%20Launch%20Was%20Called%20Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBoeing's%20Starliner%20space%20capsule%20was%20set%20for%20its%20inaugural%20test%20flight%20with%20NASA%20astronauts%2C%20including%20Indian-origin%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20on%20board.%20However%2C%20the%20launch%20was%20automatically%20halted%20mere%20minutes%20before%20liftoff%20due%20to%20a%20computer%20abort%20system%2C%20marking%20another%20indefinite%20delay%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20countdown%20to%20launch%20had%20reached%20the%20final%20stages%20when%20the%20automatic%20abort%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20ground%20system%20computer%20responsible%20for%20coordinating%20the%20last%20moments%20before%20liftoff.%20With%20just%20three%20minutes%20and%2050%20seconds%20left%20on%20the%20clock%2C%20the%20system%20issued%20a%20command%20that%20stopped%20the%20launch%20sequence.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20Starliner%20capsule%20itself%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20good%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20Of%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20latest%20postponement%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20of%20last-minute%20technical%20issues%20that%20teams%20had%20been%20working%20through.%20Initially%2C%20NASA%20and%20Boeing%20planned%20for%20a%20potential%20launch%20window%20today.%20However%2C%20NASA%20decided%20against%20it%2C%20stating%20that%20additional%20time%20was%20needed%20to%20assess%20the%20issue%20thoroughly.%20The%20next%20available%20windows%20are%20June%205%20and%20June%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20really%20close%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Stich%2C%20manager%20of%20NASA's%20commercial%20crew%20program%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20it's%20a%20little%20disappointing%2C%20we%20were%20all%20excited.%20This%20is%20kind%20of%20the%20way%20spaceflight%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETory%20Bruno%2C%20CEO%20of%20United%20Launch%20Alliance%20(ULA)%2C%20the%20joint%20venture%20between%20Boeing%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%20that%20owns%20the%20Atlas%20V%20rocket%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20issue%20could%20be%20a%20hardware%20malfunction%20or%20a%20network%20communication%20problem%20between%20the%20three%20computers%20managing%20the%20automated%20launch%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing's%20journey%20with%20the%20Starliner%20has%20been%20fraught%20with%20challenges.%20The%20first%20attempt%20to%20send%20an%20uncrewed%20Starliner%20to%20the%20ISS%20in%202019%20failed%20due%20to%20software%20and%20engineering%20problems.%20A%20second%20attempt%20in%202022%20succeeded%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20this%20first%20crewed%20test%20mission.%20Previous%20delays%2C%20including%20a%20faulty%20pressure%20valve%20and%20various%20engineering%20issues%2C%20have%20already%20pushed%20the%20timeline%20back%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoeing's%20Hopes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20astronauts%20Barry%20%26quot%3BButch%26quot%3B%20Wilmore%20and%20Sunita%20%26quot%3BSuni%26quot%3B%20Williams%20were%20strapped%20into%20their%20seats%20for%20several%20hours%20before%20the%20mission%20was%20halted.%20Technicians%20safely%20assisted%20them%20out%20of%20the%20capsule%2C%20and%20they%20were%20returned%20to%20quarantine%20to%20await%20the%20next%20launch%20attempt.%20This%20mission%20is%20critical%20for%20Boeing%2C%20as%20it%20aims%20to%20establish%20the%20Starliner%20as%20a%20reliable%20option%20for%20ferrying%20astronauts%20to%20the%20ISS%20and%20beyond%2C%20competing%20against%20SpaceX's%20Crew%20Dragon%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Starliner%20program%2C%20under%20a%20%244.2%20billion%20contract%20with%20NASA%2C%20has%20seen%20its%20budget%20swell%20to%20around%20%244.5%20billion%20due%20to%20various%20setbacks.%20For%20Boeing%2C%20success%20with%20the%20Starliner%20is%20crucial%2C%20not%20only%20for%20its%20space%20ventures%20but%20also%20to%20recover%20from%20crises%20in%20its%20commercial%20aeroplane%20manufacturing%20operations.%20NASA%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20views%20the%20Starliner%20as%20a%20key%20component%20of%20its%20strategy%20to%20diversify%20its%20astronaut%20transport%20options%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20its%20broader%20Artemis%20program%20aimed%20at%20returning%20humans%20to%20the%20Moon%20and%20eventually%20to%20Mars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20launched%2C%20the%20Starliner%20is%20expected%20to%20dock%20with%20the%20ISS%20approximately%2024%20hours%20later.%20The%20mission%20includes%20tasks%20such%20as%20testing%20manual%20control%20capabilities%20and%20evaluating%20the%20spacecraft's%20performance%20as%20a%20potential%20safe%20haven.%20After%20about%20a%20week%20at%20the%20ISS%2C%20the%20astronauts%20will%20return%20to%20Earth%2C%20landing%20with%20the%20help%20of%20parachutes%20and%20airbags%20in%20the%20US%20Desert%20Southwest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717299060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fs4236tc8_sunita-williams-_625x300_02_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-sunita-williams-boeing-starliner-space-launch-was-called-off-5798126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Boeing's%20Starliner%20space%20capsule%20was%20set%20for%20its%20inaugural%20test%20flight%20with%20NASA%20astronauts%2C%20including%20Indian-origin%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20on%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-sunita-williams-boeing-starliner-space-launch-was-called-off-5798126%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-sunita-williams-boeing-starliner-space-launch-was-called-off-5798126%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-sunita-williams-boeing-starliner-space-launch-was-called-off-5798126%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sushant's%20sister%20visits%20Kedarnath%20ahead%20of%20his%20death%20anniversary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717298749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110632801%2Cimgsize-128892.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsushant-singh-rajputs-sister-shweta-singh-vists-kedarnath-ahead-of-his-4th-death-anniversary-i-felt-an-urge-to-hug-him%2Farticleshow%2F110632810.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110632810.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20sister%20visits%20'Kedarnath'%20in%20order%20to%20feel%20close%20to%20Sushant.%20She%20meditates%20like%20him%20and%20meets%20the%20Sadhu%20who%20had%20also%20met%20Sushant%20in%20Kedarnath%20during%20his%20trip!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20May%20Sweep%20Polls%2C%20But%20Fall%20Short%20Of%20370-Seat%20Target%2C%20Predict%20Bookies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBookies%20in%20Delhi%20have%20predicted%20a%20thumping%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20but%20put%20them%20well