from%20its%20prebiotic%20fiber%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%2C%20which%20seeks%20%245%2C000%2C000%20in%20financial%20damages%2C%20says.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20even%20if%20a%20consumer%20were%20to%20do%20this%2C%20Poppi's%20high%20sugar%20content%20would%20offset%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20of%20these%20purported%20gut%20health%20benefits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20an%20inulin-based%20diet%20could%20cause%20%26quot%3Binflammation%20and%20even%20liver%20damage%26quot%3B%20with%20doses%20as%20low%20as%2010%20grams%20per%20day%20and%20demands%20a%20jury%20trial%20to%20determine%20whether%20Poppi%20has%20broken%20the%20law%20with%20its%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoppi's%20sodas%2C%20which%20have%20gone%20viral%20in%20the%20years%20since%20their%202018%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-crowdfund-tiktok-shark-tank-investor-accredited-campaign-valuation-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20sell%20for%20%242.49%20a%20can%20through%20the%20manufacturer's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20colorful%20cans%20of%20apple%20cider%20vinegar-infused%20sodas%20have%20become%20so%20popular%20that%20the%20suit%20noted%20Forbes%20reporting%20from%20March%20that%20the%20brand%20sits%20at%20a%2019%25%20market%20share%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0more%20than%201.5x%20that%20of%20Coke%20products%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20is%20the%2011th-fastest%20growing%20beverage%20brand%2C%20beating%20out%20companies%20like%20Gatorade%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliquid-death-punk-water-review-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiquid%20Death%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Poppi%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoppi-soda-gut-health-claims-mislead-consumers-new-lawsuit-alleges-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717290599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665bacdbcc442a2f676d03b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoppi-soda-gut-health-claims-mislead-consumers-new-lawsuit-alleges-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20the%20marketing%20for%20Poppi%2C%20a%20soda%20aimed%20at%20health-conscious%20consumers%2C%20makes%20misleading%20claims%20about%20its%20gut%20health%20benefits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A57%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoppi-soda-gut-health-claims-mislead-consumers-new-lawsuit-alleges-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20Executives%20Unlikely%20To%20Be%20Charged%20Over%20Deadly%20Crashes%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBoeing%20executives%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20criminally%20charged%20over%20fatal%20crashes%20in%202018%20and%202019%20that%20killed%20346%20people%20as%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations%20has%20likely%20passed%2C%20U.S.%20Justice%20Department%20officials%20told%20victims'%20family%20members%20in%20a%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20were%20corroborated%20by%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20gathering%20on%20Friday%20and%20correspondence%20reviewed%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20for%20prosecuting%20most%20federal%20crimes%20is%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20found%20in%20mid-May%20that%20Boeing%20violated%20a%202021%20deferred%20prosecution%20agreement%20(DPA)%20that%20had%20shielded%20the%20company%20from%20a%20criminal%20charge%20arising%20from%20the%20fatal%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20agreed%20to%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20dismiss%20the%20charge%20of%20conspiring%20to%20defraud%20the%20U.S.%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%20as%20long%20as%20Boeing%20abided%20by%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%20over%20a%20three-year%20period%20ending%20Jan.%207%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20in-flight%20blowout%20two%20days%20before%20the%20agreement%20expired%20exposed%20ongoing%20safety%20and%20quality%20issues.%20A%20panel%20blew%20off%20a%20new%20Boeing%20737%20MAX%209%20jet%20during%20a%20Jan.%205%20Alaska%20Airlines%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20until%20June%2013%20to%20outline%20any%20disagreements%20with%20the%20department's%20finding%20that%20it%20violated%20the%202021%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20have%20until%20July%207%20to%20inform%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20Texas%20of%20its%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20honored%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20Boeing%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20is%20weighing%20several%20options%2C%20including%20whether%20to%20prosecute%20Boeing%20or%20extend%20the%20DPA%20by%20a%20year.%20Officials%20could%20also%20enter%20into%20a%20new%20DPA%20or%20reach%20a%20non-prosecution%20agreement%20that%20does%20not%20involve%20court%20supervision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20could%20also%20seek%20to%20negotiate%20a%20plea%20deal%20with%20Boeing%20over%20the%202021%20fraud%20charge%20or%20take%20the%20company%20to%20trial%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20could%20also%20face%20charges%20over%20its%20behavior%20during%20the%20three-year%20term%20of%20the%20DPA%2C%20though%20officials%20have%20not%20found%20evidence%20of%20any%20felonies%20committed%20during%20that%20period%2C%20prosecutors%20told%20the%20victims'%20families%2C%20according%20to%20the%20source%20familiar%20with%20meeting.