dation%20Bilderberg%20Meetings%2C%20led%20by%20a%20steering%20committee%20of%20elite%20members%20from%20government%2C%20business%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20the%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20meeting%20in%20May%201954%20was%20held%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20The%20Netherlands%2C%20from%20which%20the%20meeting%20gets%20its%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRepresentatives%20from%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20political%20and%20cultural%20fields%20were%20invited%20to%20informal%20discussions%20to%20help%20create%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20complex%20forces%20and%20major%20trends%20affecting%20Western%20nations%20in%20the%20difficult%20postwar%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Bilderberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbilderbergmeetings.org%2Fbackground%2Fbrief-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnown%20group%20members%20have%20included%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Henry%20Kissinger%20and%20David%20Rockefeller%2C%20who%20was%20once%20chairman%20of%20the%20Chase%20corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca199ffd-1b7e-497f-a33e-b01b2f28846c%5C%22%3ERecent%20Meetings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPast%20meetings%20have%20been%20hosted%20in%20Portugal%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-the-secret-bilderberg-meeting-of-the-worlds-top-bankers-2011-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwitzerland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20the%20years%2C%20the%20annual%20Meetings%20have%20become%20a%20forum%20for%20discussion%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20trade%20to%20jobs%20to%20technology%2C%20from%20monetary%20policy%20to%20investment%2C%20and%20from%20ecological%20challenges%20to%20the%20task%20of%20promoting%20international%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group's%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20secrecy%2C%20the%20group%20does%20put%20o