lt%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20relishing%20the%20meal%2C%20Sandeep%20also%20got%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20harsh%20lives%20of%20hill%20women.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20women%20were%20working%20under%20the%20MGNREGA%20scheme%20as%20labourers%20and%20their%20job%20was%20to%20dig%20ground%20and%20lift%20boulders%20%E2%80%94%20all%20for%20a%20daily%20wage%20of%20Rs%20270.%20The%20work%20was%20said%20to%20guarantee%20100%20days%20of%20employment%20in%20a%20year%20but%20the%20system%20was%20corrupt%20at%20the%20village%20level.%20There%20was%20no%20surety%20on%20timely%20payments%20and%20number%20of%20working%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HimFla%20sources%20pink%20rock%20salt%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20spices%20and%20herbs%20from%201%2C000%20small%20farmers%20in%20Uttarakhand.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351424%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHimFla%20sources%20pink%20rock%20salt%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20spices%20and%20herbs%20from%201%2C000%20small%20farmers%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20now%20knew%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202013%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20commercialise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310963%2Fsashi-bahuguna-raturi-uttarakhand-pisyu-loon-salt-namakwali-video%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflavoured%20salt%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20provide%20employment%20to%20rural%20women.%20Along%20with%20his%20childhood%20friends%20Sourabh%20Pant%20and%20Yogendra%20Singh%2C%20he%20launched%20HimFla%20%E2%80%93%20short%20for%20Himalayan%20Flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20inception%20of%20a%20multi-crore%20business%20with%20just%20Rs%20160%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20flavoured%20salt%2C%20Sandeep%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20kitchens%20are%20mostly%20modular%3B%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Esilbattas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20been%20replaced%20by%20grinders%20and%20mixers.%20Although%20electronic%20machines%20have%20made%20our%20lives%20easier%2C%20the%20taste%20achieved%20through%20grinding%20in%20%3Cem%3Esilbattas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%E2%80%99t%20be%20got%20through%20modern%20equipment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20salt%20is%20pounded%20without%20any%20heat.%20This%20keeps%20the%20natural%20taste%20and%20flavours%20intact.%20In%20a%20grinder%2C%20the%20food%20is%20just%20cut%20into%20very%20fine%20pieces%20and%20not%20pounded%20to%20be%20properly%20mixed.%20When%20you%20use%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20actually%20blending%20all%20the%20oils%20of%20the%20herbs%20and%20spices%20together%20to%20enhance%20the%20flavours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20was%20determined%20to%20revive%20the%20traditional%20practice%20of%20using%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20With%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201