%9COur%20product%20range%20includes%20classic%20flavours%20like%20vanilla%2C%20butterscotch%2C%20and%20chocolate%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fruit%20flavours%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20pitaya%2C%20tender%20coconut%2C%20mango%2C%20chikoo%2C%20and%20jackfruit.%20We%20also%20offer%20innovative%20flavours%20like%20charcoal%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20striking%20black-coloured%20icecream.%20This%20unique%20flavour%20is%20a%20standout%20in%20our%20product%20lineup.%20We%20produce%20the%20charcoal%20by%20burning%20coconut%20shells%20and%20then%20using%20the%20resulting%20charcoal%20as%20an%20ingredient%20in%20our%20charcoal%20icecream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20our%20existing%20range%2C%20we%20have%20recently%20introduced%20a%20traditional%20milk%20category%20%E2%80%94%20featuring%20camel%20milk%20icecream%2C%20goat%20milk%20icecream%2C%20and%20donkey%20milk%20icecream.%20We%20are%20proud%20to%20be%20the%20first%20brand%20to%20offer%20these%20unique%20categories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaheswaram%20Kumar%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20thing%20about%20their%20delicious%20icecream%20is%20the%20various%20unique%20flavours.%20I%20personally%20love%20the%20jackfruit%2C%20chilly%20guava%20and%20coconut-flavoured%20icecreams.%20There%20is%20no%20guilt%20to%20have%20as%20much%20as%20you%20want%20as%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20sugar%20and%20are%20made%20with%20organic%20butter%20and%20oil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20has%20around%2070%20physical%20outlets%2C%20which%20include%20both%20franchise%20and%20company-owned%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7bZzxboZC3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7bZ