ion%20activity%20occurs%20below%20the%20ground%2C%20alleviating%20the%20problems%20of%20water%20stagnation%2C%20bad%20odour%20and%20risk%20of%20mosquito%20breeding.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20his%20foundation%20has%20worked%20with%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%20government%20colleges%20in%20Sundargarh%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Sri%20Aurobindo%20Ashram%20in%20Nainital%2C%20recycling%20over%206%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20year.%20This%20year%2C%20Prashant%20expects%20the%20number%20to%20increase%20to%2010%20lakh%20litres%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20is%20self-funded%20and%20Prashant%20charges%20the%20schools%2Fcolleges%20only%20for%20the%20civil%20work.%20He%20hopes%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20consultation%20service%20with%20an%20annual%20maintenance%20contract%20like%20the%20ones%20that%20water%20filter%20companies%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20working%20model%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288886%2Fsustainable-farmhouse-in-gujarat-gets-zero-power-bills-recycles-greywater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreywater%20recycling%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20two%20school%20projects%2C%20Prashant%20borrowed%20money%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20build%20the%20solutions.%20He%20is%20now%20working%20with%20village%20administrations%20and%20the%20ashram%20on%20a%20revenue-based%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20people%20can%20pay%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20a%20small%20fee.%20We%20want%20to%20generate%20revenue%20instead%20of%20depending%20on%20funds%20from%20larger%20players%20as%20this%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20fund%20initiatives%20in%20villages%20and%20communities%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prashant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20though%2C%20he%20is%20managing%20as%20his%20wife%20has%20a%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20keeps%20him%20going%20is%20the%20response%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20has%20been%20very%20positive%20everywhere%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been.%20Right%20from%20villages%20to%20cities%2C%20people%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20stagnant%20water%20and%20want%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prashant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20this%20water%20conservationist%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20living%20has%20to%20be%20more%20than%20making%20money%2C%20it%20has%20to%20involve%20fulfilling%20the%20needs%20of%20people%20who%20are%20within%20your%20sphere%20of%20influence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20email%20Prashant%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Apash.childrensearth%40gmail.comor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epash.childrensearth%40gmail.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20call%20him%20on%209711086014.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Prashant%20Sharma%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716901564000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIMG-20231120-WA0044-min-1716894257.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351304%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prashant%20Sharma%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20London%20to%20launch%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20called%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Action%20for%20Child%20and%20Earth%20Foundation%E2%80%99.%20Through%20this%2C%20he%20provides%20greywater%20recycling%20solutions%20to%20schools%2C%20colleges%20and%20other%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351304%2Fchennai-bengaluru-water-crisis-prashant-sharma-grey-water-recycling-in-schools%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20After%20Paradise